## 003 Messanger application

	After setting up the basic running project in 002Messanger, we are going to add our own classes and resources in this project.
	
	#### What do we learn
	
	* Create a new Resource
	* @Path annotation on the class of the resource
	* @GET and @POST annotations
	* @Produces(MediaType.TEXT_PLAIN) and @Produces(MediaType.APPLICATION_XML)
	* @XmlRootElement to support xml conversion
	
### Reference
https://javabrains.io/courses/javaee_jaxrs/lessons/Creating-A-Resource	